<p>In my hunt for a fun project that I could build my best friend Jenn for her birthday, I came across this instructable for an <a href="http://www.instructables.com/id/IKEA-Infinity-Mirror/">infinity mirror</a>.
It consists of a deep frame or shadowbox, some colorful LEDs, a 100% reflective mirror, and a semi-transparent mirror, otherwise known as a ‘one way’ mirror.</p>
